1308
01:39:50,487 --> 01:39:54,560
There seems to be a staggeringly
high proportion of hay fever sufferers...

1309
01:39:54,647 --> 01:39:57,400
..and they're right next to
the damn flowers.

1310
01:39:57,487 --> 01:39:59,557
So we're moving the congregation.

1311
01:39:59,647 --> 01:40:01,956
