I think I've fooled them so far.

1319
01:40:32,967 --> 01:40:36,039
When people think you're stupid,
they're less suspicious.

1320
01:40:36,127 --> 01:40:37,958
What's your advice?

1321
01:40:38,047 --> 01:40:41,198
You've got three choices:
one - go ahead with it...

1322
01:40:42,927 --> 01:40:45,919
